{"tid":397494,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"GTA V 兄弟會(BHHK) 幫會招募","createTime":"2017-09-12T13:51:36.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-22T12:58:53.000Z","uid":43697,"like":4,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"f9cc90dd09060b56858bff2dd59a581b9c69c68c","tid":397494,"uid":43697,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-12T13:51:36.000Z","msg":"歡迎各位巴打絲打加入我們<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n幫會 BrotherHoodHongKong<br />\n<br />\n幫會SocialClub<br />\n<a href=\"https://zh.socialclub.rockstargames.com/crew/brotherhood_hongkong\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.socialclub.rockstargames.com%2Fcrew%2Fbrotherhood_hongkong&d=QIHojuRPl3dnuWgQfyJodMn%2FdpYTMnF8ODxps2tmzCA%3D&h=77fa658d\" target=\"_blank\">https://zh.socialclub.rockstargames.com/crew/brotherhood_hongkong</a><br />\n<br />\n我們致力打造一個團結、融洽的GTA幫會<br />\n歡迎各位巴打、絲打成為我們一份子<br />\n可以一起解打劫任、CEO.摩托幫.地堡偷貨送貨以及遊玩GTA各項模式(例:競速、團隊死鬥等),亦會不定時舉辦幫會活動<br />\n<br />\n基本守則:<br />\n<br />\n* 嚴禁人身攻擊,嚴禁惡意言論<br />\n<br />\n* 如見到同幫會成員被惡意追殺理應出手相助<br />\n<br />\n* 禁止幫會成員間打鬥(得到雙方同意除外)<br />\n<br />\n* 取得幫會成員懸賞金前請先過問,並得到同意<br />\n<br />\n* 舉辦幫會活動時請配合主辦者的指示<br />\n<br />\n* 批准加入幫會後,必須將「BrotherHoodHongKong」設為活動幫會<br />\n<br />\n----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------<br />\n申請方法<br />\n<br />\n必須先把Social Club統計資料設定為開啟,並以Line主動聯絡kappaho1118或ira1115留下以下資料,其他方法暫一律不獲批准!<br />\n<br />\n1. Social Club ID<br />\n2. PSN ID<br />\n3. 有無MIC<br />\n<br />\n----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------<br />\nGTA5 軍事<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/12/214642_beccbb6b5b0133b02a5bb86d39ca99cd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F12%2F214642_beccbb6b5b0133b02a5bb86d39ca99cd.jpg&h=acbcc71a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/12/214652_6dd97fdc97dd05ba580d3e4479bd2ac5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F12%2F214652_6dd97fdc97dd05ba580d3e4479bd2ac5.jpg&h=e5224125&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/12/214700_3470dc66bb7990e7d2b3a0e87b105664.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F12%2F214700_3470dc66bb7990e7d2b3a0e87b105664.jpg&h=a898bbd7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n幫會車聚 28-07-2017<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/12/214848_aaa068d0ed0d10fd1603722dfa095d66.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F12%2F214848_aaa068d0ed0d10fd1603722dfa095d66.jpg&h=9e411266&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/12/214857_decb4586960ce575ccf41db0247d55d6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F12%2F214857_decb4586960ce575ccf41db0247d55d6.jpg&h=2cea226f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/12/214916_016d2e2a0af2b705c0f485b88d09c86f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F12%2F214916_016d2e2a0af2b705c0f485b88d09c86f.jpg&h=5f9bd6eb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/12/215031_189145007b960497a823380835ec2d25.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F12%2F215031_189145007b960497a823380835ec2d25.jpg&h=c3ec6f83&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/12/215048_4c5b0d48b9602e300bdb6c7bc0403dad.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F12%2F215048_4c5b0d48b9602e300bd